p: Several studies list the constituents of the EODa, where its composition can be variable, such as in the study by [ 24], where mainly oxygenated terpenes and sesquiterpenes (Î±-terpinene 61.04%, 4-carene 13.55% and p-cymene 12.94%) were identified, meanwhile the study by (9) registered cis and trans ascaridol (35.4% and 26.0%, respectively), and p-cymene (29.2%), as the major constituents.
